26:12.505 --> 26:13.671
[gasps]

26:13.756 --> 26:16.290
<i> ♪ gave up fighting for ♪</i>

26:18.344 --> 26:21.712
♪<i> what I claim I adore ♪</i>

26:21.797 --> 26:25.766
<i> ♪ butterfly, butterfly, I ♪</i>

26:26.886 --> 26:29.219
♪<i> thought you were my ♪</i>

