<i> circle 'round your soul ♪</i>

27:01.087 --> 27:02.219
[phone ringing]

27:04.473 --> 27:06.223
[davis]<i> hey.</i>
<i> You've reached davis west.</i>

27:06.309 --> 27:07.591
<i> Leave a message</i>
<i> at the beep.</i>

27:07.677 --> 27:09.426
-[beep]
-hey, you.

27:11.097 --> 27:12.763
Thank you.

27:12.848 --> 27:16.317
This was so sweet of you.

27:21.073 --> 27:23.157
I have, um...

27:23.275 --> 27:25.693
I've seen you love
when it was easy.

27:27.530 --> 27:31.448
I've seen you love
when it was hard.

27:31.534 --> 27:36.820
When love was
the only thing
left for us to do.

27:36.922 --> 27:39.840
We've taken on the challenges

27:40.760 --> 27:42.876
and joys of life.

27:43.946 --> 27:46.347
Can't believe I'm in
this place with you.

27:47.516 --> 27:49.717
I never thought
I'd be here again.

27:50.586 --> 27:54.021
But here we are.

27:56.275 --> 27:58.008
And I'm happy.

27:58.110 --> 28:01.511
♪<i> thought you were my ♪</i>

28:01.614 --> 28:04.865
♪<i> thought you were my ♪</i>

28:06.285 --> 28:07.868
I love you, too.

28:28.958 --> 28:31.392
Darla said guidry was here.
What's going on?

28:31.994 --> 28:33.444
Nothing.

28:34.246 --> 28:36.480
They just tearing up the land.

28:36.582 --> 28:38.198
Deputy gave them
a warrant today.

28:38.284 --> 28:39.750
-That's what they doing.
-What?

28:39.835 --> 28:42.986
Yeah,<i> blessings and blood</i>
gave them the idea

28:43.089 --> 28:45.339
that there was some
bodies still buried here.

28:46.075 --> 28:47.708
That was just speculation.

28:47.793 --> 28:50.544
A memory I couldn't explain,
a metaphor.

28:50.629 --> 28:53.046
It's not true.
We know that now.

28:53.132 --> 28:56.350
Well, I'm sorry this
is happening but I promise you
I'll get into this.

28:57.520 --> 28:58.769
I'll make it right.

29:12.868 --> 29:14.902
-[violet] all right, baby.
We good?
-Thanks vi.

29:14.987 --> 29:16.286
[violet] thank you.

29:17.123 --> 29:18.972
-Hey, harold!
-Hey!

29:19.074 --> 29:20.841
-All right.
You all good? Thank you.
-Thank you.

29:20.943 --> 29:22.409
[violet] have a good one.

29:23.629 --> 29:25.129
Look at you.

29:25.214 --> 29:29.166
I think you have put together
about 100 of these boxes.
I think we're good.

29:30.052 --> 29:31.752
I can refill
the napkin container.

29:31.837 --> 29:33.587
No, they not running low.

29:34.223 --> 29:37.641
Is there something
I can do for you, miss vi?

29:37.726 --> 29:39.676
Yes.

29:39.762 --> 29:43.063
You can start divorce
proceedings on that no-good
husband of yours.

29:45.317 --> 29:49.436
You need to start
putting your life
back together, baby.

29:50.322 --> 29:52.156
Now, look.

29:52.241 --> 29:55.325
I know it ain't easy.
I've been there.

29:55.995 --> 30:00.080
But you start with baby steps
to make things better.

30:01.333 --> 30:03.083
You think about your son.

30:04.286 --> 30:06.587
He deserves a better life.

30:07.506 --> 30:08.539
I got something!

30:08.624 --> 30:10.740
Oh. Oh. Oh.
Whoa, whoa, yeah,
the big one too!

30:10.843 --> 30:12.459
Come on! Reel it in!
Reel it in!

